org.cyclops.cyclopscore.recipe.custom.api

Interface IRecipe<I extends IRecipeInput,O extends IRecipeOutput,P extends IRecipeProperties>

  • Type Parameters:
    I - The type of the recipe input of all recipes associated with the machine.
    O - The type of the recipe output of all recipes associated with the machine.
    P - The type of the recipe properties of all recipes associated with the machine.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Recipe

    public interface IRecipe<I extends IRecipeInput,O extends IRecipeOutput,P extends IRecipeProperties>
    Interface for recipes that can be registered with ISuperRecipeRegistry.
